patthana23.30:1.1_0: Namahaggataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā mahaggato kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.30:2.1_0: Namahaggataṁ naakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā paritto akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.30:3.1_0: Naparittaṁ naabyākataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca paritto abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.30:3.1_1: (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha …pe… avigate cha.
